- No.

56
00:02:57.790 --> 00:03:00.620
Did you travel four months
ago to red lodge. Montana?

57
00:03:03.620 --> 00:03:04.880
Yes.

58
00:03:06.750 --> 00:03:09.280
Are you currently engaged
