121
00:05:50.130 --> 00:05:51.650
No arrests were made in the end.

122
00:05:51.790 --> 00:05:53.920
Ok. so violence is his specialty.

123
00:05:54.050 --> 00:05:56.116
- Well. it used to be.
- He's moved up in their ranks.

124
00:05:56.140 --> 00:05:57.286
They're hierarchical.

125
00:05:57.310 --> 00:05:59.116
Love a hate group with an org chart.

126
00:05:59.140 --> 00:06:02.490
- What's he doing in New York?
- That's an excellent question.

127
00:06:02.620 --> 00:06:04.166
He's never been to the U.S. before.

128
00:06:04.190 --> 00:06:06.686
So if he's here. that means he could be

129
00:06:06.710 --> 00:06:08.516
