- what. strike up a conversation?

157
00:07:32.670 --> 00:07:34.516
It's just two anxious dads
sharing a life-changing moment.

158
00:07:34.540 --> 00:07:36.566
Well. you've got the anxious part down.

159
00:07:36.590 --> 00:07:38.826
Why don't you?

160
00:07:38.850 --> 00:07:41.436
Because. bill. this is so
far outside my wheelhouse.

161
00:07:41.460 --> 00:07:43.590
not even I can pull this one off.

162
00:07:43.720 --> 00:07:45.746
No argument there.

163
00:07:56.430 --> 00:07:59.626
- First-time dad?
- Yeah.

164
00:07:59.650 --> 00:08:03.376
Hey. congratulations. Me too.

165
00:08:03.400 --> 00:08:05.360
My wife. she's having a c-section.

166
00:08:05.490 --> 00:08:07.206
Ok.

167
00:08:07.230 --> 00:08:10.026
- Where are you from?
- Belarus.

168
00:08:10.050 --> 00:08:12.246
- Wow. never been.
- Is it...

169
00:08:12.270 --> 00:08:15.206
