193
00:09:13.940 --> 00:09:16.550
- He cut the ID tag off.
- Ok. did you see him go past?

194
00:09:16.690 --> 00:09:18.016
Yeah. he was just here a minute ago.

195
00:09:18.040 --> 00:09:19.576
Was he... was he carrying anything?

196
00:09:19.600 --> 00:09:20.576
A duffel bag.

197
00:09:20.600 --> 00:09:22.056
Said he was going to the cafeteria.

198
00:09:22.080 --> 00:09:23.276
We have to shut this place down now.

199
00:09:23.300 --> 00:09:24.300
Call an Amber alert.

200
00:09:26.700 --> 00:09:30.050
- This is a code pink.
- Repeating. we have a code pink.

201
00:09:33.660 --> 00:09:36.426
Hey! Hey!

202
00:09:47.760 --> 00:09:49.086
So aleks kovadenko brought
a pregnant woman with him

203
00:09:49.110 --> 00:09:50.500
