207
00:09:59.560 --> 00:10:03.926
Sophia ankov. 20. from
gorna bela rechka. Bulgaria.

208
00:10:03.950 --> 00:10:06.406
No criminal history. but
she did lie to customs

209
00:10:06.430 --> 00:10:08.650
