- Ok. Is she in the path?

210
00:10:08.780 --> 00:10:10.740
Does she have a
boyfriend. brothers. sisters?

211
00:10:10.870 --> 00:10:12.676
Not according to our sources.

212
00:10:12.700 --> 00:10:14.196
She has no known associates affiliated

213
00:10:14.220 --> 00:10:16.026
