217
00:10:22.010 --> 00:10:25.166
Well. he's gonna need
medical intervention.

218
00:10:25.190 --> 00:10:27.850
The question is. what
is a suspected terrorist

219
00:10:27.980 --> 00:10:30.036
- doing stealing a newborn baby?
- Yeah.

220
00:10:30.060 --> 00:10:31.566
And we're gonna have to
find this guy. because none

221
00:10:31.590 --> 00:10:33.420
- of this is adding up for me.
- Yeah.

222
00:10:36.770 --> 00:10:38.486
So do you know how we
can get in touch with aleks?

223
00:10:38.510 --> 00:10:41.096
No. I want to find him too.

224
00:10:41.120 --> 00:10:43.316
- Is he the baby's father?
- No.

225
00:10:43.340 --> 00:10:44.276
Ok. so how... how do you know him?

226
00:10:44.300 --> 00:10:45.650
