244
00:11:39.390 --> 00:11:42.416
Ok. Ok. here.

245
00:11:42.440 --> 00:11:45.816
If you help us find aleks.
we'll get your baby back.

246
00:11:45.840 --> 00:11:47.466
All right?

247
00:11:47.490 --> 00:11:50.100
Aleks promised my baby

248
00:11:50.230 --> 00:11:54.816
